refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public stringMemcached::getResultMessage
Memcached::getResultMessage returns a string that describes the result code of the last executed Memcached method.

  &reftitle.examples;



    Memcached::getResultMessage example


<?php
$m = new Memcached();
$m->addServer('localhost', 11211);

$m->add('foo', 'bar'); // first time should succeed
$m->add('foo', 'bar');
echo $m->getResultMessage(),"\n";
?>


    &example.outputs;


